name: Fish Robber: MAD Stray Cat
description:
Whops! He's realy mad now!
Gonna rob one bucket of fresh salmon, and plus rob your heart! Aw! He can't wait to be yours!

I will donate 100% of the sales of this art for abandoned stray cats and dogs in Indonesia. If you are willing to help, please share to others or buy. Bless your kindness!
